Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.200
Welcome to Telugu Tastebuds

00:00:03.420 --> 00:00:07.520
Today we are going to cook Ginger Chutney.

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:11.580
Take a pan , heat it and add some oil

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:19.020
Add some fenugreek seeds

00:00:19.020 --> 00:00:23.400
Add some mustard seeds

00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:29.200
Fry them

00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:34.340
Add some cumin seeds and 5 whole red chilli

00:00:34.340 --> 00:00:42.540
Add some urad dal (from Indian store)

00:00:42.540 --> 00:00:51.840
Add some ginger in it

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:55.560
Add a spoon of turmeric powder

00:00:55.560 --> 00:01:01.080
Add some hing  (Asafoetida) and mix it will

00:01:01.080 --> 00:01:08.220
Add some curry leaves

00:01:08.220 --> 00:01:11.540
Let it cool for 15 mins

00:01:11.540 --> 00:01:20.880
Grind it  by adding some salt

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:25.760
Add tamarind juice

00:01:25.900 --> 00:01:38.940
Add some jaggery

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:51.440
After grinding, take it into a bowl

00:01:54.280 --> 00:02:02.680
Thats it, Ginger Chutney is ready

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:09.580
Please subscribe and share. Thank you

